OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,FWARNING: The following article
OL,7,Fcontains references to suicide.
OL,9,FThe friends and family of an American
OL,10,Fman encouraged to take his own life
OL,11,Fonline have shared their memories of
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,FTravis Dyer, from Louisiana in America
OL,15,Fwas goaded into shooting himself in
OL,16,FOctober 2024 by Dylan Phelan, from
OL,17,FLeeds, over the social network
OL,18,Fplatform Discord which is primarily
OL,19,Fused by video game players to
OL,20,Fcommunicate.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
