OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,FTravis had struggled with his mental
OL,7,Fhealth for years having lost both his
OL,8,Fmother and baby sister in a car
OL,9,Faccident when he was ten.
OL,11,FHe lived with his grandfather Eddie
OL,12,FMoran, who told ITV Calendar, "If you
OL,13,Fmet him, you'd like him. He had a lot
OL,14,Fof hopes."
OL,16,FThree months after Travis died his
OL,17,Ffriends were given access to his phone
OL,18,Fwhere they learned why he had decided
OL,19,Fto take his life.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,FHis friend Skylar Coan said: "What we
OL,7,Ffound was a Discord server full of
OL,8,Fpeople.
OL,10,F"It was supposed to be support and you
OL,11,Fknow people talking in neutrality
OL,12,Fabout their feelings and coping with
OL,13,Fsuicide.
OL,15,F"But instead what they did was they
OL,16,Ftook a vulnerable person and forced
OL,17,Fthem to commit suicide and manipulated
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,20,F"He was my brother and I love him. I
OL,21,Fmiss him every day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,F"Nothing feels real without him, and
OL,7,Fit's, it's genuinely heartbreaking to
OL,8,Ftry and continue to exist without him."
OL,10,F"I have nothing but hate and rage. I
OL,11,Fwant nothing but the worst for these
OL,12,Fpeople."
OL,14,FA close family friend of Travis,
OL,15,FAndrea Benoit, added: "He was alive
OL,16,Fand then they just encouraged him to
OL,17,Fend it and be so final and then
OL,18,Fcelebrate that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,F"It was disgusting. I just can't
OL,7,Fimagine that kind of evil is in
OL,8,Fexistence."
OL,10,FWhile Dylan Phylan faces jail time,
OL,11,Ftwo others are also suspected to be
OL,12,Finvolved. The police investigation has
OL,13,Fbecome a Trans-Atlantic affair.
OL,15,FLt. Blake Tabor of Terrebonne Parish
OL,16,FSheriff's Office said: "People like
OL,17,FDylan need to understand that law
OL,18,Fenforcement is very far reaching, and
OL,19,Fwe will do what is necessary to make
OL,20,Fsure that you are adjudicated by law"
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
