PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,FAlex Johnson, senior prosecutor for
OL,7,Fthe British Crown Prosecution service
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a deeply disturbing
OL,9,Fcase involving the sustained
OL,10,Fexploitation of a vulnerable young man
OL,11,Fthrough an online platform.
OL,13,F"Dylan Phelan did not merely witness
OL,14,Fwhat happened ` he actively
OL,15,Fparticipated in goading Travis Dyer to
OL,16,Ftake his own life, intending that he
OL,17,Fwould do so.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781385839
OL,3,CFriends and family remember man goaded
OL,4,Cto suicide online
OL,6,F"His actions were calculated, cruel,
OL,7,Fand had devastating consequences. Our
OL,8,Fthoughts remain with Travis Dyer's
OL,9,Ffamily and friends. We hope today's
OL,10,Foutcome provides them with a measure
OL,11,Fof justice."
OL,13,FDylan Phylan was sentenced at Leeds
OL,14,FCrown Court on 12 June to 6 years for
OL,15,Fencouraging suicide.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the online platform
OL,18,FDiscord said: "Real-world violence of
OL,19,Fany kind is devastating and content
OL,20,Fthat encourages or glorifies this
OL,21,Fbehavior has no place on Discord.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
